# 本地开发认证配置示例
# 将此内容添加到你的 ~/.npmrc 文件中

# 1. 先创建 Personal Access Token:
#    https://gitlab.longbridge-inc.com/-/user_settings/personal_access_tokens
#    权限勾选: api, write_repository, read_repository

# 2. 复制下面的配置到 ~/.npmrc，并替换 <YOUR_TOKEN>
//gitlab.longbridge-inc.com/api/v4/projects/4872/packages/npm/:_authToken=<YOUR_TOKEN>

# 示例:
# //gitlab.longbridge-inc.com/api/v4/projects/4872/packages/npm/:_authToken=glpat-abc123xyz456
